history.content:
Pass (or no pass) your thoughts on P/NP over to the Blue & Gold Yearbook at http://tinyurl.com/bg-pnp-form! We're interested in hearing from students about your opinions on how the policy changes affect you, thoughts or concerns that you would like to vocalize, and how you plan on utilizing the changes in your courseload. 

----

As the Blue & Gold Yearbook, we provide coverage of events, issues, and trends within the Berkeley community and include graduating seniors’ portraits. Our mission is to truthfully encapsulate the current, unique Berkeley identity—its culture, events, and lifestyle—as students, for the students. To stay updated with what we do, follow us on Instagram and Facebook. Questions? Email us at info.bgyearbook@gmail.com!
history.subject: P/NP Questionnaire for Blue & Gold Yearbook
